title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You might develop a growing awareness that you are playing a new role with colleagues and friends now. Perhaps more of your pals look to you for personal advice or you become more instrumental in the inner workings of team projects. However the energy unfolds, the Aries Full Moon beams into your 11th House of Community, recalibrating your relationships and revitalizing your social network. You can sow plenty of goodness when youre reaping the fruits of intentional self-love. A regular practice of gratitude is a powerful leadership skill. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
